quran[23{c,v,t}:
89,1,Fajar ki qasam
89,2,aur das raton ki
89,3,aur juft aur taaq ki
89,4,aur raat ki jab jaane lagey
89,5,aur be shak yeh cheeze aqalmandon ke nazdeek qasam khanay ke Laiq hain ke ( kafiroon ko zaroor azaab ho ga )
89,6,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke tumahray perwar-digaar ne Aad ke sathkiyakiya
89,7,( jo ) Iram ( kehlate they itnay ) daraaz qad
89,8,ke tamam malik mein aisay peda nahi hue they
89,9,aur smod ke sath (kiyakiya ) jo wadiِ ( qura ) mein pathar tarashtain they ( aur ghar banatay ) they
89,10,aur firaon ke sath (kiyakiya ) jo khaimay aur maikhain rakhta tha
89,11,yeh log mulkon mein sarkash ho rahay they
89,12,aur un mein bohat si kharabian karte they
89,13,to tumahray perwar-digaar ne un par azaab ka kora nazilkiya
89,14,be shak tumhara perwar-digaar taak mein hai
89,15,magar ensaan ( ajeeb makhlooq hai ke ) jab is ka perwar-digaar is ko aazmaata hai to usay izzat deta aur Nemat bakhshta hai. to kehta hai ke ( ahaa ) mere perwar-digaar ne mujhe izzat bakhsh
89,16,aur jab ( doosri terhan ) aazmaata hai ke is par rozi tang kar deta hai to kehta hai ke ( haae ) mere perwar-digaar ne mujhe zaleelkiya
89,17,nahi balkay tum log yateem ki khatir nahi karte
89,18,aur nah maskeen ko khana khilanay ki targheeb dete ho
89,19,aur meeras ke maal samaitt kar kha jatay ho
89,20,aur maal ko bohat hi Aziz rakhtay ho
89,21,to jab zameen ki bulandi coat coat ko pust kar di jaye gi
89,22,aur tumhara perwar-digaar ( jalva farma ho ga ) aur farishtay qitaar bandh bandh kar aa mojood hon ge
89,23,aur dozakh is din haazir ki jaye gi to ensaan is din mutnabba ho ga magar tanbih ( se ) usay ( faida ) kahan ( mil sakay ga )
